overview: When Katie hears that her best friend Hazels love life is taking a turn downhill, she invites Hazel to a swingers party with her and her husband Seth. Apprehensive at first, Hazel soon falls under the sensual charm of Katies husband, and Katie gets into bed with her BFFs husband, Calvin. Kenzie and James plan a swingers weekend to the California wine country and invite a couple they met at a festive orgy. All four enjoy wine tasting but Kenzie cant wait to whisk Jay away for a passionate roll between the sheets and it doesnt take Kamryn long to start seducing James.
title: Swingers Getaway 5
